{"type": "article", "id": 2236, "title": "极简钱包", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:35:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222259xJq0dAcCSVEniymj.JPG", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Nothing Fancy by <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/chieh\" target=\"_blank\">Chieh Ting Huang</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t没有任何针线缝合的皮质钱包，手工课作品一般，灵感来自经典的把纸钞卷成一卷用橡皮筋捆起来的收纳方法。除了钱包，设计理念还用到了零钱袋、iPhone套、卡包和护照夹等等物品上，成为收纳日常零碎的解决方法。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135132n5wqu8lbaE3vDeJB.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135132BczkWwT2N68iSsmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135133OaiRhWXxcBvoZTUy.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135133CfMZAw9ju6xvIzFV.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135134wckbZvxQEqloLRmM.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}